Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.97,0:00:04.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens, I'm still your partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.81,0:00:07.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today, we go back 10 years, to when Ran and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.70,0:00:09.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,embarked on a dangerous adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.23,0:00:10.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Recognizing that single truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.68,0:00:12.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a child with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.19,0:00:14.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.04,0:02:03.04,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Library
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.61,0:02:24.42,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Book The Adventures of Sherlock Holmes by Conan Doyle
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:32.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, you can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.88,0:02:34.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be so loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.59,0:02:36.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:39.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, if you keep yawning while reading his work,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:44.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the one you love so much, Conan Doyle, will roll over in his grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:47.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you expect?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.40,0:02:52.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I read all of the mysteries in here while I was in elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.23,0:02:53.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's nothing left.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:56.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.74,0:03:01.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This world is full and brimming with mysteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:04.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What he... That voice just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.04,0:03:06.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The deal back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:08.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, it was that guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:10.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What with that scared look?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:13.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:14.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:17.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kojima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, what're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:19.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't stand on books!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.31,0:03:24.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if I don't, I can't reach the books up here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.71,0:03:26.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei, help!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:31.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:34.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't feel sorry for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:36.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:38.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which book do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.74,0:03:40.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll get it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.66,0:03:43.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:46.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me put this one back first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.13,0:03:51.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something in the back of the bookshelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:53.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.30,0:03:56.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's a dead snake?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.26,0:03:59.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know, not all the way out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:17.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Young Kudo Shinichi's Adventure, Part One!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.41,0:04:24.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez, don't say things like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.50,0:04:26.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really thought that it was a snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.25,0:04:28.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like a wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.38,0:04:33.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it looks like leather.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.09,0:04:36.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why would someone put this in the back of this book shelf?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.72,0:04:38.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's look inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:40.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There may be money in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.85,0:04:41.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.52,0:04:49.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like there's just a piece of paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:51.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.61,0:04:54.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something written on it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:55.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.49,0:04:57.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.82,0:04:59.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Class 1-A, Mouri Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.45,0:05:02.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How'd you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.54,0:05:05.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It really say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.25,0:05:07.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, let's look...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.25,0:05:11.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That's really what it says, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:15.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course I'd know, Ran and I were...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:21.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I mean... Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r} told me about\Nsomething that happened a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:23.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.64,0:05:29.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, something strange, suspicious, and mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:32.28,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It all started 10 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.38,0:05:34.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,10 years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.71,0:05:34.63,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Wait up, Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.69,0:05:38.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think we should be going to the school this late...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.11,0:05:39.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I told you to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:42.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll get in trouble for sneaking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.03,0:05:45.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll expose the monster on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.83,0:05:50.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, if you go by yourself, you'll get eaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.13,0:05:57.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stupid! There's no such thing as a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.63,0:06:00.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} heard about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.22,0:06:02.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It appears in the library when there's a full moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:07.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a ghost with a creepy voice and a strange hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.39,0:06:10.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a full moon out tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.73,0:06:12.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This'll be interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:16.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:22.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop slowing me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.03,0:06:24.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.25,0:06:30.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew everything would be locked, we can't get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:31.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:38.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why's it unlocked?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.43,0:06:45.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I unlocked it before I left today, since the\Nsecurity guard doesn't check carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.10,0:06:50.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, let's head for the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.73,0:06:52.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.09,0:07:21.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone's in the library!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.43,0:07:23.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.73,0:07:33.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? It's just the security guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.19,0:07:35.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:39.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like he's been drinking again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.07,0:07:43.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Great. Since he just checked, he won't be back for awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.02,0:08:13.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See? No ghosts here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:16.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's that sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:25.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a ghost with a hat on near the window!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.41,0:08:26.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.99,0:08:28.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stupid, look closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.58,0:08:32.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The curtain has slipped off some of its hooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.75,0:08:39.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It only appears on a full moon because the\Nmoonlight makes the shadow form.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.38,0:08:44.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That weird "laughing" sound is the wind\Nthat's coming through the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.47,0:08:48.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All most ghost stories lack is on explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.73,0:08:50.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.14,0:08:52.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, that resolves everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.77,0:08:56.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that really so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.78,0:09:02.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.62,0:09:06.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What you're doing is reading the preview on the cover of the book,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.99,0:09:09.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,simply pretending you can see everything at its finest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.23,0:09:15.55,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Book Arséne Lupin: Gentleman Burglar by Maurice LeBlanc
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:13.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This world is deep...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.04,0:09:16.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and brimming with mysteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.71,0:09:19.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.22,0:09:27.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.97,0:09:29.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am your...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:31.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sibling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.19,0:09:32.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.10,0:09:36.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I should be more specific.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:38.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm your younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.90,0:09:41.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My younger brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.86,0:09:44.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.24,0:09:46.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Run, go get the security guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.30,0:09:47.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:52.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? It won't open!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.63,0:09:54.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.71,0:09:55.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.88,0:09:58.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've cast a spell on that door
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.12,0:10:01.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll only listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.59,0:10:02.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.88,0:10:06.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Careful, I didn't come to fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:11.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've actually come to challenge you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.69,0:10:17.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Try to find the treasure that's in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.69,0:10:19.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.82,0:10:21.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you can find it, you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.32,0:10:24.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can then have the treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:26.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:28.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll even tell you who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.41,0:10:32.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whether you accept my challenge is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.00,0:10:36.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you do accept, I'll lift the spell on the door and let you go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.79,0:10:42.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you do not, you'll spend the rest of your lives in this cold, dark room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.30,0:10:44.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.59,0:10:46.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really love seeing blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.22,0:10:49.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And anything red.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.02,0:10:52.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're not scared of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.98,0:10:56.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're not gonna listen to a bad man like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.73,0:10:59.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh my, what a fiery little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:01.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.24,0:11:03.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said I accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.45,0:11:05.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll play your game.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.37,0:11:08.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's you all right, Kudo Shinichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.99,0:11:10.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.93,0:11:23.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.46,0:11:26.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You! What're you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.06,0:11:28.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:33.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:55.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Shinichi, are you really going to accept?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.16,0:11:56.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.10,0:12:00.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad has always told me to never back down from a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.02,0:12:04.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that man just then was like a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.52,0:12:07.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't care if it was the devil or some demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.03,0:12:10.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just wanna know who he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.86,0:12:14.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what this code means.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.28,0:12:21.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Shinichi, if that guy uses his magic around us again, he may kill us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.54,0:12:23.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.75,0:12:27.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember, he casted a spell on the door so it wouldn't open!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:30.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stupid, take o closer look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.51,0:12:33.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see the map next to the door, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.01,0:12:37.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's fishing line that goes through the\Nhook attached to the top of the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:45.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we came in, he used the fishing line to push\Nthe map against the door so it wouldn't open.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.86,0:12:51.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All of this was done from where he was sitting originally.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.36,0:12:56.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy said a lot to try and scare us,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.70,0:12:59.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but all he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.95,0:13:05.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is some clumsy magician that forgot to hide his trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.46,0:13:10.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing, Shinichi! You're just like Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:11.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.55,0:13:15.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right then, Holmes{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.72,0:13:18.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know what the code says?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:21.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know what it means yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.02,0:13:21.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but it says...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.39,0:13:26.56,Signs,,0,0,0,,Note: Kanji characters are the last you learn when learning\NJapanese, As they're the most complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.39,0:13:26.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,FIND HAIDO'S STRANGE BEGINNINGS\N"Haido no... Okori wo... Chinmeyo."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.09,0:13:26.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:32.29,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Note Some kanji characters are rare, so it's likely that\Nsome 1st graders would not be able to read them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:30.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Okori wo chinemeyo"? Is that really how it's read?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.32,0:13:34.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I see "okuru" in a lot of novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.07,0:13:37.75,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"Chinkon" means "requiem" and is written with two kanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.07,0:13:37.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for "chin", I saw "chin-kon-ka" on one of my mom's CD's.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:40.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I asked her about it so I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:44.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure on adult will know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:46.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's ask our dads!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.54,0:13:47.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.13,0:13:49.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell any of the adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.21,0:13:52.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a battle between me and him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.06,0:14:03.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That boy read...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.77,0:14:09.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Ikori wo shizumeyo" as "Okori wo chinmeyo"!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.28,0:14:11.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.70,0:14:14.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Shinichi guy's such an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.12,0:14:18.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was really young then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.41,0:14:20.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not like you could have then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:20.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.37,0:14:25.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you expect? He was in first grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.33,0:14:28.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that Shinichi boy reminds me of Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.92,0:14:31.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:32.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:34.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened next?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.93,0:14:36.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry and finish!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:39.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those two got home safe, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.64,0:14:42.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r} said that next...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.10,0:14:44.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.15,0:14:47.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where have you been this whole time!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.77,0:14:51.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, I forgot something at school, so I had to...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:52.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't lie to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:54.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's that Shinichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} again, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:55.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.12,0:14:58.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:15:00.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen him much lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:03.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of kid is Yukiko raising over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.33,0:15:08.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe Yuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} is trying the hands-off approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:10.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear, you're going to work now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:14.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there was a murder at a warehouse in the Haido Port.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:17.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Inspector Megure and I are going to check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.22,0:15:19.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be careful out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.68,0:15:21.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It could be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:23.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You too, make sure the doors are locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:27.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That thief hos been taking things everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:31.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, I'm the wife of a police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.24,0:15:32.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:34.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, take care of Ran for me, Eri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.99,0:15:39.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.33,0:15:41.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.20,0:15:43.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Eri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:44.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:49.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it! I'm not letting you go to bed until you spill it, Shinichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.71,0:15:54.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder what you were doing taking a girl to school after dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.84,0:15:57.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you already, didn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:59.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I forgot something there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:02.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of answer is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:04.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:06.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They both got home safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:09.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But still, Yuusaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:12.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, this isn't o police interrogation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:15.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's not going to say anything with you being so angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:18.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, quell your anger and remain calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:20.75,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Yuusaku says, "Ikari wo shizumete" here, as the "quell your anger"\Npart, as compared to shinichi's "okori wo chinmeyo" from earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:20.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,QUELL - ANGER\N"Ikari wo shizumeru"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.45,0:16:22.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, how do you write that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:25.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,QUELL - ANGER\N"Ikari wo shizumeru"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:26.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it written like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:28.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:33.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a code that my teacher mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:37.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a mean teacher, giving such hard kanji to first graders.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:42.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must be an interesting teacher who is fond of riddles.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:43.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Riddles?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:47.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure what they want to get across by mentioning Haido.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:49.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, say,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.82,0:16:51.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,why don't we go to the beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:52.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That'd be great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:56.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haido Port?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.12,0:17:00.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The code says to go to Haido Port, Shinichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:01.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.54,0:17:07.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,QUELL THE ANGER OF HAIDO\N"Haido no ikari wo shizumeyo" refers to Haido Port and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.29,0:17:13.30,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Note "Drop the anchor" can be pronounced the same\Nas "quell the anger" just written differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.29,0:17:09.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Dropping the anchor."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:14.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Shinichi, didn't you say it was "Okori wo chinmeyo" last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.89,0:17:16.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Did I now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:19.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But is this all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:26.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The guy that gave you the code snuck into\Nthe school and waited for you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:27.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should just tell the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.94,0:17:31.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not too late to call them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:33.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's just wait until we've solved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:38.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, and I'm sorry for making you come out so early, Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:41.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no, I'm actually glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.29,0:17:44.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been awhile since I saw you two getting along.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.12,0:17:49.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys used to always come by and play before school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:54.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hadn't seen you all together in awhile, so I was worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:57.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd gotten into a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.18,0:17:59.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's nothing like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.18,0:18:00.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:01.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:06.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at all the police cars...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:09.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something happen-here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:12.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, my Dad mentioned something last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.82,0:18:14.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A murder at Haido Port!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.20,0:18:17.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, that guy could'be the criminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.87,0:18:19.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, he couldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:24.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This happened around the time you all were at the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:29.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard the criminal was caught before daybreak, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.84,0:18:35.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, what we really need to find out is why\Nthat guy wanted you guys to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.22,0:18:38.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he'll come by if we wait for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.81,0:18:39.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:41.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And anything red.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.56,0:18:43.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.27,0:18:45.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be red.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:46.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.02,0:18:48.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The lights flash red!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:51.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The professor already told us, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:54.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The case has nothing to do with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:57.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He couldn't have known the police cars would be parked here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:19:01.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means it must be something that's always here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.03,0:19:01.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something that's red.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.92,0:19:09.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fire hydrant!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:13.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't look like anyone's here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:17.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's peeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:24.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a piece of paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.93,0:19:26.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's another one that's hard to read.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:27.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.15,0:19:33.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Clear the allegations against Toriya, and demolish the liver of Goroukou."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:39.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We know "Toriya" is referring to the Toriya District, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.12,0:19:44.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't be sure what "clear the allegations" means.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.08,0:19:46.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's probably another riddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:52.10,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Note Mito Koumon was historical figure later featured\Nin a famous TV drama with the same name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:50.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is the Goroukou mentioned referring to Koumon{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.63,0:19:51.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.84,0:19:55.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Professor, "clear the allegations" would mean\Nto prove that someone wasn't the criminal, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.72,0:19:56.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.20,0:20:03.80,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Note In japan, black means guilty while white means innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:19:58.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The criminal must be the black one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:01.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My Dad says it a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:04.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He says: "The criminal is the black one!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.27,0:20:05.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Black?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.85,0:20:08.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The criminal is the black one?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.27,0:20:09.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The opposite is white...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:12.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,White, white, white...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.28,0:20:14.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Toriya Castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.07,0:20:19.20,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Note "Shiro" in Japanese means both "castle" and the color "white".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.07,0:20:18.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then let's head to where the castle was once!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.07,0:20:21.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, we need to head to the floodgates near the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.49,0:20:22.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The floodgates?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:24.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to the castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.41,0:20:29.83,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,NOTE "Goroukou" was the name he assumed as he travelled about\Nthe countryside writing wrong, disguised as an old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.41,0:20:29.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Goroukou" comes from Mito Koumon, while\N"liver" points us to the internal organs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:33.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To "demolish" his "liver" means to remove the middle...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.71,0:20:36.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, by removing the middle kanji, "to" and "kou", from Mito Koumon...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:39.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.93,0:20:42.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\b1}MIZU MON\N{\b0}That leaves you with the two kanji for "water" and "gate".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:46.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since it's near Toriya Castle, it has to be the Toriya Floodgates!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.81,0:20:54.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, these are the floodgates...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.45,0:20:57.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't see any weird red things...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.87,0:21:09.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew we should gone to the castle first
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.37,0:21:13.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if that were so, "clear the allegations against\NToriya" is all he would have had to write on the paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.63,0:21:16.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means there must be something here, near he floodgates...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:20.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or maybe something between where the\Ncastle once was and the floodgates...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.64,0:21:21.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something red...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.56,0:21:25.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The railroad crossing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.99,0:21:39.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you see anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.22,0:21:41.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.62,0:21:42.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.87,0:21:46.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it were something you could find before the\Nlights turned red, it'd defeat the purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.37,0:21:51.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means it has to be something that only shows after it turns red...
